Antonio Prieto Martin writes:
> When will open5066 be a product that we might consider ready for systems 
> integration?

Depends on maturity level and functionality you are looking for.

Could you please briefly describe your application and which
features of STANAG 5066 you would require?

Please describe your developer skills, i.e. how much help I can
expect from you?

Currently our goal is to have first over the air communications
happen in June (using non ARQ mode) and after that work on
the arq mode. By end of summer it should be in pretty good shape.

